Markdown is powered by [Markdoc](https://markdoc.dev). This is an example to demonstrate all the basic Markdown syntax. You can author content using the familiar Markdown syntax you already know.

## Inline formatting

Bold: **This text is bold**.

Italics: _This text is italics_.

Strikethrough: You can ~~strikethrough~~ text.

Inline code: You can add code like this `const hello = "world"`.

```md
Bold: **This text is bold**.

Italics: _This text is italics_.

Strikethrough: You can ~~strikethrough~~ text.

Inline code: You can add code like this `const hello = "world"`.
```

