## Code blocks

Syntax highlighting is done using [Shiki](https://github.com/shikijs/shiki). You can customise to whichever theme you want from the [plenty available Shiki themes](https://github.com/shikijs/shiki/blob/main/docs/themes.md).

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Example HTML5 Document</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>Test</p>
  </body>
</html>
```

````md
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Example HTML5 Document</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>Test</p>
  </body>
</html>
```
````

